headline: Banks Must Educate as They Innovate: Over a Third of UK Consumers Say Financial Services AI is Moving Too Fast, FIS Research Shows
summary: LONDON, December 10, 2025--New UK research from FIS reveals that consumer confidence is failing to keep pace with bank innovation, creating an AI trust gap.
